              leaf console monitor for c-icap-leaf service

This is part of the c-icap server project. More information about c-icap
server you can find here:
   http://c-icap.sourceforge.net/

Implements leaf console monitor for the leaf intercept module for the c-icap server. Currently the following services are implemented:
  - leaf console monitor program for providing top-like server statistics and live statistics for the c-icap server and the leaf icap intercept module as well as statistics for the mysql storage server.

For support, use the following resources:
 - General discussion related to c-icap server:
   c-icap-users@lists.sourceforge.net
 - Basic installation and configuration instructions:
   https://sourceforge.net/p/c-icap/wiki/configcicap/

For more information see the file README.pdf for more detailed description of the 
leaf monitor program and c-icap-leaf module and how they work and can be configured.

